"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:3.1.6.3\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">3.1.6.3</span> 標題：牆（wall）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： כֹּתֶל</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： kothel)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song2:9\">SNG 2:9</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Aramaic</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">蘭：כְּתַל</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： kethal)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra5:8\">EZR 5:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:5\">DAN 5:5</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： קִיר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： qir)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:37\">LEV 14:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:37\">LEV 14:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:39\">LEV 14:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:11\">1SA 18:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:10\">1SA 19:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:10\">1SA 19:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:25\">1SA 20:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:22\">1SA 25:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:34\">1SA 25:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:11\">2SA 5:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:13\">1KI 5:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:6\">1KI 6:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:15\">1KI 6:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:15\">1KI 6:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:27\">1KI 6:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:27\">1KI 6:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:29\">1KI 6:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:10\">1KI 14:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:11\">1KI 16:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:21\">1KI 21:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:10\">2KI 4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs9:8\">2KI 9:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs9:33\">2KI 9:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:2\">2KI 20:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr14:1\">1CH 14:1</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0409_wall.jpg\" alt=\"安裝在牆上的石塊\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">安裝在牆上的石塊 (MM, Public domain, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>牆是構成建築物或房間一側的立面。牆支撐著房間的天花板或建築物的屋頂。這裡的討論會區分建築物中的這種牆和城牆（参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.13.3.1 城牆、外郭、城垛 (city wall, rampart, battlement)&lt;REALIA:3.13.3.1&gt;</a> ）或邊界牆（参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.6 邊界牆、圍牆、圍欄、柵欄 (boundary wall, fence)&lt;REALIA:3.6&gt;</a> ）。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>希伯來文<em>qir</em> 既可以指建築物的外牆，也可以指內牆。如果目標語言有詞語分別表示這兩種不同的牆，翻譯者要留意上下文，以選擇合宜的用詞。例如，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:13\">1KI 5:13</a> （《和》4:33）提到「在牆上長出的牛膝草」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 直譯），那裡的「牆」更有可能是指房子的外牆，而不是內牆。</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:22\">1SA 25:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:34\">1SA 25:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:10\">1KI 14:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:11\">1KI 16:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:21\">1KI 21:21</a> 和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs9:8\">2KI 9:8</a> 中，有一個希伯來文短語直譯作「對著牆小便的人」。這個短語意指男子，因此大多數譯本都譯為「男子」或「男性」。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:11\">2SA 5:11</a> 和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr14:1\">1CH 14:1</a> 記載，推羅王希蘭派「石匠」（“masons”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> ）到所羅門那裡，該詞在希伯來文中的字面意思為「牆石工／牆石切割工」。這些匠人塑造石頭的形狀，使其能夠嚴密地、整齊地堆砌成一面牆。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 譯為“stone masons”（「石頭匠人」），<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 譯為“stone workers”（「石頭工人」）。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
